Title: It is hard to recommend Google Cloud
Description:
Google Domains A year back, I had to migrate my domain after Google decided to shut down Google Domains. I had to, not only, painfully setup multiple side-projects sub-domain mappings again on a new domain registrar but also re-verify my domain and re-create those mappings on Google Cloud Run.
Google Container Registry Google Container Registry is shutting down in 2025. It has been replaced with a new project called Artifact Registry.

Title: Uber Caught Overcharging? How Having Credits in Your Account Might Be Costing You - View from the Wing
Description: My hypothesis was that Uber seemed to be picking a higher price because I had credits in my account. I might be willing to spend more because my 'real' out of pocket cost was less, and those credits were trapped anyway.  I decided to use my Uber credits for Uber Eats instead. That pricing seemed normal.
